<li>
<div><div> <a href="/blog/interviews/when-sensibility-art-meets-pragmatism-science-conversation-tlotlo-tsamaase" hreflang="en"><img loading="lazy" src="/sites/default/files/styles/medium_thumbnail/public/Tlotlo-Tsamaase-w.jpg?itok=s09tG4TW" width="250" height="175" alt="A photograph of Tlotlo Tsamaase" typeof="foaf:Image" class="img-fluid image-style-medium-thumbnail" />
</a>
</div></div><div class="views-field views-field-field-richtitle"><p class="field-content"><a href="https://www.worldliteraturetoday.org/blog/interviews/when-sensibility-art-meets-pragmatism-science-conversation-tlotlo-tsamaase">When the Sensibility of Art Meets the Pragmatism of Science: A…</a>
</p></div><div class="views-field views-field-field-author"><span class="views-label views-label-field-author field-name-field-blogauthor">By</span><span class="field-content field-name-field-blogauthor"><a href="/author/darlington-chibueze-anuonye" hreflang="en">Darlington Chibueze Anuonye</a>
</span></div>
</li>
</ul>
